node.text: Hahhaha 🤣🤣🤣. Makes me laugh this pic 🤣.
Cuteness overload

Motherhood, a journey that has often turned my life upside down, given me plenty of sleepless nights and messy hair days along the way (lucky no white hair yet but I am sure the day is coming soon!) but also one that has provided me with countless happy memorable moments and laughter in the house.
.
This Mother’s Day, Matty (and daddy) gave me a hand painted shiny Exeggcute (if you play Pokémon too you will know what this is) and the hubs promised to watch CLOY with me tonight onwards ✌️ (yes, we are super late to the game I know).
.
Happy Mother’s Day everyone! Hope it was an awesome one for you ❤️
